               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I bought the ticket of the spoons of a woman—they were in pawn for 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.—I wanted money, and pawned them again—I was the prosecutor's housekeeper, and was obliged to send him a lawyer's letter to get my money—I did not know the spoons were his till I was at Mary-lebone office.</p>
